I use {% assign category = page.url | remove:'/' | capitalize %} to get my category and {% for post in site.categories[category] %} to filter my posts.

But if I can get query string parameters I only need to create one html file like this:

---
layout: blog
title: {{ page.url.params.category }}
permalink: /category/
---
This page is {{ page.url.params.category }} for categories.
